The paper proposes a deep neural network-based architecture for product recommendation in e-commerce, which involves modeling temporal online user behaviors and generating recommendations for anonymous users. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Cybersecurity (cs.CY), and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI). Among these, cs.IR and cs.LG are the most likely categories, as they are directly related to the paper's focus on recommendation systems and deep learning techniques.
